name: All the Cheeses in NYC
description:
“The initial concept was to create a maze game, connecting all the architectural elements with a multitude of passageway, zip lines etc… until I got side tracked with the Cheeses invasion. A perfect example of “Playing” with the creative process. You never know where it will take you.”

Rotring pen and markers on paper
5000 x 5000 px

by Guillaume Cornet AKA @guillustration
